         <Common_Consequences>
            <Consequence>
               <Scope>Availability</Scope>
               <Impact>Reduce Performance</Impact>
               <Impact>DoS: Resource Consumption (CPU)</Impact>
	       <Note>This issue can make the product perform more slowly, possibly in ways that are noticeable to the users.  If an attacker can influence the amount of computation that must be performed, e.g. by triggering worst-case complexity, then this performance problem might introduce a vulnerability.</Note>
            </Consequence>
         </Common_Consequences>
		 <Observed_Examples>
